In a small bowl, stir together the salad dressing, basil, garlic and red pepper flakes. Set aside. In a large pot of salted boiling water, cook pasta until al dente, rinse under cold water and drain. In a large bowl, combine the pasta, albacore, tomato, avocado and red onion. Add dressing and toss together to evenly coat. Line four plates with lettuce leaves, spoon on salad and garnish with olive slices.